@page "/organisational-structure"
@namespace MACDEF.Client.Pages

<div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-[#8B4513] to-[#D2691E] text-white py-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Organisational Structure</h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-100">How MACDEF is organized and governed</p>
    </div>
</div>

<main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto py-16 px-6">
    <!-- Overview Section -->
    <section class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-gray-900">MACDEF Structure Overview</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-8">
            The organisational structure of MACDEF is designed to ensure effective governance, operational efficiency, and community engagement. The structure comprises four main components working together to serve the Ma'di community:
        </p>
        <div class="bg-[#F5E6D3] border-l-4 border-[#8B4513] p-6 rounded mb-8">
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
                <li class="flex items-start">
                    <span class="font-bold text-[#8B4513] mr-3">1.</span>
                    <span>The General Assembly (GA)</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                    <span class="font-bold text-[#8B4513] mr-3">2.</span>
                    <span>The Board of Directors (BoD)</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                    <span class="font-bold text-[#8B4513] mr-3">3.</span>
                    <span>The Secretariat</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                    <span class="font-bold text-[#8B4513] mr-3">4.</span>
                    <span>The Committees (Thematic Committees)</span>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- The General Assembly -->
    <section class="mb-16">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg overflow-hidden border-t-4 border-[#8B4513]">
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-[#8B4513] to-[#A0522D] text-white p-6">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold flex items-center">
                    <i class="ri-team-line mr-3 text-3xl"></i>The General Assembly (GA)
                </h3>
            </div>
            <div class="p-8">
                <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Role & Responsibilities:</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
                    The GA is the highest governing body of MACDEF. It consists of the representation of all categories of members who have duly complied with the requirements.
                </p>
                <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Composition:</h4>
                <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                        <span class="text-[#8B4513] font-bold mr-3">•</span>
                        <span>All registered members of MACDEF in good standing</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                        <span class="text-[#8B4513] font-bold mr-3">•</span>
                        <span>Representatives from different member categories</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                        <span class="text-[#8B4513] font-bold mr-3">•</span>
                        <span>Members must comply with organizational requirements</span>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- The Board of Directors -->
    <section class="mb-16">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg overflow-hidden border-t-4 border-[#8B4513]">
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-[#8B4513] to-[#A0522D] text-white p-6">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold flex items-center">
                    <i class="ri-group-2-line mr-3 text-3xl"></i>The Board of Directors (BoD)
                </h3>
            </div>
            <div class="p-8">
                <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Role & Responsibilities:</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
                    The BoD manages the business of the Company and ensures effective governance, accountability, and strategic decision-making.
                </p>
                <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Board Composition:</h4>
                <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded mb-6 border-l-4 border-[#8B4513]">
                    <p class="text-gray-700 font-semibold mb-3">Nine (09) Members composed of people with varying skills and expertise:</p>
                    <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700 ml-4">
                        <li>• 1 Chairperson</li>
                        <li>• 1 Secretary</li>
                        <li>• 7 Additional Members</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Required Board Expertise:</h4>
                <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                    <div class="bg-[#F5E6D3] p-4 rounded">
                        <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Technical Expertise:</p>
                        <ul class="space-y-1 text-sm text-gray-700">
                            <li>✓ Legal</li>
                            <li>✓ Human Resources (HR)</li>
                            <li>✓ Accounting & Audit</li>
                            <li>✓ Fundraising/Proposal Writing</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-[#F5E6D3] p-4 rounded">
                        <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Non-Technical Attributes:</p>
                        <ul class="space-y-1 text-sm text-gray-700">
                            <li>✓ Selflessness</li>
                            <li>✓ Integrity</li>
                            <li>✓ Commitment</li>
                            <li>✓ Patriotic dedication to Ma'di culture</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mt-6 mb-4">Board Diversity Requirements:</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
                    The Board must ensure diversity across:
                </p>
                <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700 ml-4">
                    <li>• Knowledge and skills/disciplines</li>
                    <li>• Professional background and experience</li>
                    <li>• Gender representation</li>
                    <li>• Cultural perspective and background</li>
                </ul>
                <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mt-6 mb-4">Board Committees:</h4>
                <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-3 mt-4">
                    <div class="bg-gray-100 p-4 rounded">
                        <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">• Executive & Governance Committee</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-gray-100 p-4 rounded">
                        <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">• Nomination & HR Committee</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-gray-100 p-4 rounded">
                        <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">• Membership Committee</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-gray-100 p-4 rounded">
                        <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">• Finance Committee</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-gray-100 p-4 rounded col-span-2">
                        <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">• Audit, Risk & Compliance Committee</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- The Secretariat -->
    <section class="mb-16">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg overflow-hidden border-t-4 border-[#8B4513]">
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-[#8B4513] to-[#A0522D] text-white p-6">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold flex items-center">
                    <i class="ri-briefcase-line mr-3 text-3xl"></i>The Secretariat
                </h3>
            </div>
            <div class="p-8">
                <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Role & Responsibilities:</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
                    The Secretariat undertakes active day-to-day participation in the affairs of MACDEF. It comprises the Project Management Team and administrative personnel working toward achieving the organization's objectives.
                </p>
                <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Secretariat Composition:</h4>

                <div class="bg-[#F5E6D3] p-6 rounded mb-6 border-l-4 border-[#8B4513]">
                    <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Leadership:</p>
                    <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700 ml-4">
                        <li>• Executive Director (ED) - Appointed by the Board</li>
                        <li>• Heads of Thematic Clusters (HTC) - Appointed by the Board</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-[#F5E6D3] p-6 rounded mb-6 border-l-4 border-[#8B4513]">
                    <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Administrative Team (under Executive Director):</p>
                    <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700 ml-4">
                        <li>• Head of HR and Administration</li>
                        <li>• Administrative Secretary</li>
                        <li>• Accounts Assistant</li>
                        <li>• Office Assistant</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Thematic Clusters Structure:</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
                    The Secretariat is organized into four thematic clusters encompassing 12 thematic areas:
                </p>

                <div class="space-y-4">
                    <div class="border-l-4 border-[#8B4513] pl-6 py-4 bg-gray-50 rounded">
                        <h5 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">A. Natural Resources & Economic Cluster</h5>
                        <ul class="space-y-1 text-gray-700 ml-4">
                            <li>a) Human and Animal Health Thematic Area</li>
                            <li>b) Agro-forestry and Ethno-botany/Ethno-agronomy Thematic Area</li>
                            <li>c) Environmental Management and Natural Resources Thematic Area</li>
                            <li>d) Economic Development Thematic Area</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <div class="border-l-4 border-[#8B4513] pl-6 py-4 bg-gray-50 rounded">
                        <h5 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">B. Social Development Cluster</h5>
                        <ul class="space-y-1 text-gray-700 ml-4">
                            <li>a) History, Roots and Culture Thematic Area</li>
                            <li>b) Education and Social Development Thematic Area</li>
                            <li>c) Justice, Peaceful Coexistence & Conflict Resolution Thematic Area</li>
                            <li>d) Gender Mainstreaming and Transformation Thematic Area</li>
                            <li>e) Technology and Ethno-technology Thematic Area</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <div class="border-l-4 border-[#8B4513] pl-6 py-4 bg-gray-50 rounded">
                        <h5 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">C. Voice & Accountability Cluster</h5>
                        <ul class="space-y-1 text-gray-700 ml-4">
                            <li>a) Research and Development Thematic Area</li>
                            <li>b) Monitoring and Evaluation Thematic Area</li>
                            <li>c) Information and Community Mobilisation Thematic Area (Ma'di Community Associations and Initiatives)</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <div class="border-l-4 border-[#8B4513] pl-6 py-4 bg-gray-50 rounded">
                        <h5 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">D. Human Resources & Administration Unit</h5>
                        <ul class="space-y-1 text-gray-700 ml-4">
                            <li>a) Human Resources, Administration and Governance</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- The Committees -->
    <section class="mb-16">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg overflow-hidden border-t-4 border-[#8B4513]">
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-[#8B4513] to-[#A0522D] text-white p-6">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold flex items-center">
                    <i class="ri-list-check-3 mr-3 text-3xl"></i>The Committees (Thematic Committees)
                </h3>
            </div>
            <div class="p-8">
                <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Role & Responsibilities:</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
                    Thematic Committees are formed under each Thematic Area of MACDEF. They fall within the Secretariat framework and perform specialized functions in coordination with the Executive Director and Heads of Thematic Clusters.
                </p>

                <div class="bg-blue-50 border-l-4 border-blue-500 p-6 rounded mb-6">
                    <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Committee Duties:</h4>
                    <p class="text-gray-700">
                        The duties of Thematic Committees are sanctioned by the Board and include:
                    </p>
                    <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700 ml-4 mt-3">
                        <li>• Specialized functions within their thematic area</li>
                        <li>• Coordination with the Executive Director</li>
                        <li>• Collaboration with Heads of Thematic Clusters</li>
                        <li>• Project implementation and monitoring</li>
                        <li>• Community engagement and feedback</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Committee Formation:</h4>
                <div class="bg-[#F5E6D3] p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-[#8B4513]">
                    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3">
                        Committee members are elected at an Extraordinary General Meeting (EGM) called for the purpose by popular consensus from members of MACDEF who have:
                    </p>
                    <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700 ml-4">
                        <li>• Special expertise in their thematic area</li>
                        <li>• Demonstrated skills and interest</li>
                        <li>• Commitment to MACDEF's mission and values</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mt-6 mb-4">Committee Structure:</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
                    Each Thematic Committee consists of:
                </p>
                <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
                    <div class="bg-gray-100 p-4 rounded text-center">
                        <p class="font-bold text-gray-900">Chairperson</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-gray-100 p-4 rounded text-center">
                        <p class="font-bold text-gray-900">Secretary</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-gray-100 p-4 rounded text-center">
                        <p class="font-bold text-gray-900">Members (Varied)</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm mt-4 text-center">
                    <em>The number of members varies depending on the scope and needs of each thematic area</em>
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Summary -->
    <section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-[#8B4513] to-[#D2691E] text-white rounded-lg p-12 mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">Key Organizational Principles</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
            <div>
                <h4 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3 flex items-center">
                    <i class="ri-checkbox-circle-line mr-2 text-2xl"></i>Governance
                </h4>
                <p class="text-gray-100 text-sm">
                    MACDEF operates under clear governance structures with defined roles, responsibilities, and accountability mechanisms at all levels.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h4 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3 flex items-center">
                    <i class="ri-checkbox-circle-line mr-2 text-2xl"></i>Inclusivity
                </h4>
                <p class="text-gray-100 text-sm">
                    The organization ensures diversity and inclusion across all structural levels, welcoming participation from all members of the Ma'di community.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h4 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3 flex items-center">
                    <i class="ri-checkbox-circle-line mr-2 text-2xl"></i>Collaboration
                </h4>
                <p class="text-gray-100 text-sm">
                    All structural components work in coordination to achieve MACDEF's goals of cultural preservation and community development.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h4 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3 flex items-center">
                    <i class="ri-checkbox-circle-line mr-2 text-2xl"></i>Accountability
                </h4>
                <p class="text-gray-100 text-sm">
                    Each level of the organization maintains accountability to the General Assembly and the community it serves.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Download Organogram CTA -->
    <section class="bg-gray-100 rounded-lg p-12 text-center">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Want to Learn More?</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-8">
            Download our detailed Organogram (PDF) for a visual representation of MACDEF's complete organizational structure.
        </p>
        <a href="/MACDEF-Organogram.pdf" target="_blank" class="inline-block bg-[#8B4513] text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-[#A0522D] transition">
            <i class="ri-download-2-line mr-2"></i>Download Organogram (PDF)
        </a>
    </section>
</main>

